/*
 * tests/persist/gpu/GpuIncomingUTest.cxxtest
 *
 * Phase 2 tests: fetchIncomingByType, fetchIncomingSet, loadType.
 * Verifies that the GPU parallel incoming-set scan correctly finds
 * all pairs referencing a given word.
